OL,7,FThe 42-year-old had been racing
OL,8,Fanother driver and reaching speeds of
OL,9,Fup to 100mph before losing control and
OL,10,Fsmashing into the bus stop.
OL,12,FIn December 2015, at , Mannan, from
OL,13,FRomsley in , was jailed for eight
OL,14,Fyears and banned from driving for ten
OL,15,Fyears after pleading guilty to death
OL,16,Fby dangerous driving and causing
OL,17,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,19,FHe was released in 2019 after serving
OL,20,Fhalf his sentence.
