OL,7,FLast week, Officers followed a
OL,8,FMercedes on Rubery Lane in Rubery on
OL,9,FFebruary 15th and received information
OL,10,Ffor the vehicle that suggested it was
OL,11,Fbeing driven by a disqualified driver.
OL,13,FAfter pulling over the car after
OL,14,Fseeing it go through a red light,
OL,15,FMannan confirmed he was disqualified
OL,16,Fand said he was using the vehicle to
OL,17,Ftravel for work.
OL,19,FHe also admitted not having any
OL,20,Finsurance for the vehicle.
