OL,8,Fweek, Mannan was jailed again for 12
OL,9,Fweeks and banned from driving for a
OL,10,Ffurther 770 days after pleading guilty
OL,11,Fto the offences of driving whilst
OL,12,Fdisqualified, having no insurance and
OL,13,Ffailing to comply with a red traffic
OL,14,Flight.
